&lt;p&gt;We are looking for &#39;first principles&#39; thinkers with deep understanding of the fundamentals of analog mixed-signal design who are excited to tackle the hardest, most ambiguous technical challenges at the intersection of AI, physics, and computer architecture. You will be responsible for driving invention, prototyping, and validation of the core components of our novel computing platform.&lt;/p&gt;
