&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Circuit Expertise:&lt;/strong&gt; Deep understanding of transistor-level circuit design, device physics, and noise/mismatch mechanisms in CMOS processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Scripting:&lt;/strong&gt; Proficiency with scripting languages (e.g., Python, MATLAB) for automation of design flows and data post-processing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
