&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with designing circuits in modern process nodes (22nm, 12nm and newer)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep understanding of device physics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with behavioral modeling of analog circuits and impairments for system-level verification&amp;nbsp; (e.g., in Verilog, Python, C++, MATLAB)&lt;/li&gt;
